{"schema_version":"1.7.3","id":"OESA-2024-1260","published":"2024-03-08T11:07:10Z","modified":"2025-09-03T06:19:53.744814Z","upstream":["CVE-2024-1151"],"summary":"kernel security update","details":"The Linux Kernel, the operating system core itself.\r\n\r\nSecurity Fix(es):\r\n\r\nA vulnerability was reported in the Open vSwitch sub-component in the Linux Kernel. The flaw occurs when a recursive operation of code push recursively calls into the code block. The OVS module does not validate the stack depth, pushing too many frames and causing a stack overflow. As a result, this can lead to a crash or other related issues.(CVE-2024-1151)","affected":[{"package":{"name":"kernel","ecosystem":"openEuler:20.03-LTS-SP4","purl":"pkg:rpm/openEuler/kernel&distro=openEuler-20.03-LTS-SP4"},"ranges":[{"type":"ECOSYSTEM","events":[{"introduced":"0"},{"fixed":"4.19.90-2403.1.0.0268.oe2003sp4"}]}],"ecosystem_specific":{"aarch64":["bpftool-4.19.90-2403.1.0.0268.oe2003sp4.aarch64.rpm","kernel-debuginfo-4.19.90-2403.1.0.0268.oe2003sp4.aarch64.rpm","python2-perf-debuginfo-4.19.90-2403.1.0.0268.oe2003sp4.aarch64.rpm","kernel-debugsource-4.19.90-2403.1.0.0268.oe2003sp4.aarch64.rpm","bpftool-debuginfo-4.19.90-2403.1.0.0268.oe2003sp4.aarch64.rpm","kernel-tools-devel-4.19.90-2403.1.0.0268.oe2003sp4.aarch64.rpm","kernel-tools-4.19.90-2403.1.0.0268.oe2003sp4.aarch64.rpm","perf-4.19.90-2403.1.0.0268.oe2003sp4.aarch64.rpm","python3-perf-4.19.90-2403.1.0.0268.oe2003sp4.aarch64.rpm","python3-perf-debuginfo-4.19.90-2403.1.0.0268.oe2003sp4.aarch64.rpm","python2-perf-4.19.90-2403.1.0.0268.oe2003sp4.aarch64.rpm","kernel-source-4.19.90-2403.1.0.0268.oe2003sp4.aarch64.rpm","perf-debuginfo-4.19.90-2403.1.0.0268.oe2003sp4.aarch64.rpm","kernel-tools-debuginfo-4.19.90-2403.1.0.0268.oe2003sp4.aarch64.rpm","kernel-devel-4.19.90-2403.1.0.0268.oe2003sp4.aarch64.rpm","kernel-4.19.90-2403.1.0.0268.oe2003sp4.aarch64.rpm"],"src":["kernel-4.19.90-2403.1.0.0268.oe2003sp4.src.rpm"],"x86_64":["kernel-source-4.19.90-24